overview: After meeting in their hometown of Portland, Oregon, Jinkx Monsson & Liam Krug quickly found they shared a twisted sense of humor and started writing sketches together in quarantine. This 8-episode series is born out of their weirdest ideas, featuring celebrity impersonations, a revival of Jinkx's first Snatch Game character Little Edie, and hilarious (and humiliating) new material from this duo’s wacky minds.
title: Sketchy Queens
